{"thi-ap26:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap26:0.2":"Kundalakesivagga ","thi-ap26:0.3":"Sonatheriapadana ","thi-ap26:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","thi-ap26:1.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","thi-ap26:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","thi-ap26:1.4":"kappe uppajji nayako. ","thi-ap26:2.1":"Tada setthikule jata, ","thi-ap26:2.2":"sukhita pujita piya; ","thi-ap26:2.3":"Upetva tam munivaram, ","thi-ap26:2.4":"assosim madhuram vacam. ","thi-ap26:3.1":"Araddhaviriyanaggam, ","thi-ap26:3.2":"vannesi bhikkhunim jino; ","thi-ap26:3.3":"Tam sutva mudita hutva, ","thi-ap26:3.4":"karam katvana satthuno. ","thi-ap26:4.1":"Abhivadiya sambuddham, ","thi-ap26:4.2":"thanam tam patthayim tada; ","thi-ap26:4.3":"Anumodi mahaviro, ","thi-ap26:4.4":"‘sijjhatam panidhi tava. ","thi-ap26:5.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","thi-ap26:5.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","thi-ap26:5.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","thi-ap26:5.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","thi-ap26:6.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayada, ","thi-ap26:6.2":"orasa dhammanimmita; ","thi-ap26:6.3":"Sonati nama namena, ","thi-ap26:6.4":"hessati satthu savika’. ","thi-ap26:7.1":"Tam sutva mudita hutva, ","thi-ap26:7.2":"yavajivam tada jinam; ","thi-ap26:7.3":"Mettacitta paricarim, ","thi-ap26:7.4":"paccayehi vinayakam. ","thi-ap26:8.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","thi-ap26:8.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap26:8.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap26:8.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap26:9.1":"Pacchime ca bhave dani, ","thi-ap26:9.2":"jata setthikule aham; ","thi-ap26:9.3":"Savatthiyam puravare, ","thi-ap26:9.4":"iddhe phite mahaddhane. ","thi-ap26:10.1":"Yada ca yobbanappatta, ","thi-ap26:10.2":"gantva patikulam aham; ","thi-ap26:10.3":"Dasa puttani ajanim, ","thi-ap26:10.4":"surupani visesato. ","thi-ap26:11.1":"Sukhedhita ca te sabbe, ","thi-ap26:11.2":"jananettamanohara; ","thi-ap26:11.3":"Amittanampi rucita, ","thi-ap26:11.4":"mama pageva te piya. ","thi-ap26:12.1":"Tato mayham akamaya, ","thi-ap26:12.2":"dasaputtapurakkhato; ","thi-ap26:12.3":"Pabbajittha sa me bhatta, ","thi-ap26:12.4":"devadevassa sasane. ","thi-ap26:13.1":"Tadekika vicintesim, ","thi-ap26:13.2":"‘jivitenalamatthu me; ","thi-ap26:13.3":"Cattaya patiputtehi, ","thi-ap26:13.4":"vuddhaya ca varakiya. ","thi-ap26:14.1":"Ahampi tattha gacchissam, ","thi-ap26:14.2":"sampatto yattha me pati’; ","thi-ap26:14.3":"Evaham cintayitvana, ","thi-ap26:14.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","thi-ap26:15.1":"Tato ca mam bhikkhuniyo, ","thi-ap26:15.2":"ekam bhikkhunupassaye; ","thi-ap26:15.3":"Vihaya gacchumovadam, ","thi-ap26:15.4":"‘tapehi udakam’ iti. ","thi-ap26:16.1":"Tada udakamahitva, ","thi-ap26:16.2":"okiritvana kumbhiya; ","thi-ap26:16.3":"Culle thapetva asina, ","thi-ap26:16.4":"tato cittam samadahim. ","thi-ap26:17.1":"Khandhe aniccato disva, ","thi-ap26:17.2":"dukkhato ca anattato; ","thi-ap26:17.3":"Khepetva asave sabbe, ","thi-ap26:17.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","thi-ap26:18.1":"Tadagantva bhikkhuniyo, ","thi-ap26:18.2":"unhodakamapucchisum; ","thi-ap26:18.3":"Tejodhatumadhitthaya, ","thi-ap26:18.4":"khippam santapayim jalam. ","thi-ap26:19.1":"Vimhita ta jinavaram, ","thi-ap26:19.2":"etamatthamasavayum; ","thi-ap26:19.3":"Tam sutva mudito natho, ","thi-ap26:19.4":"imam gatham abhasatha. ","thi-ap26:20.1":"‘Yo ca vassasatam jive, ","thi-ap26:20.2":"kusito hinaviriyo; ","thi-ap26:20.3":"Ekaham jivitam seyyo, ","thi-ap26:20.4":"viriyamarabhato dalham’. ","thi-ap26:21.1":"Aradhito mahaviro, ","thi-ap26:21.2":"maya suppatipattiya; ","thi-ap26:21.3":"Araddhaviriyanaggam, ","thi-ap26:21.4":"mamaha sa mahamuni. ","thi-ap26:22.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap26:22.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap26:22.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap26:23.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap26:23.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap26:23.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap26:24.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap26:24.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap26:24.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap26:25.1":"Ittham sudam sona bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap26:26.1":"Sonatheriyapadanam chattham. "}